OL,3,CArsenal miss out on Champions League
OL,4,Ctitle as PSG win on penalties
OL,6,FParis St Germain have won the
OL,7,FChampions League for the second time
OL,8,Fin a tow after beating Arsenal 4-3 on
OL,9,Fpenalties in a nail-biting final.
OL,11,FPSG's victory deprived the Gunners of
OL,12,Fwhat could have been their first
OL,13,FChampions League title in their 140-
OL,14,Fyear history ` hot off the heels of
OL,15,Ftheir first Premier League title in 22
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
