OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780251070
OL,3,CArsenal miss out on Champions League
OL,4,Ctitle as PSG win on penalties
OL,6,FSaturday's match at Budapest's Puskas
OL,7,FArena was 1-1 at the end of regulation
OL,8,Ftime and extra time, as Kai Havertz's
OL,9,Fsixth-minute opener was cancelled out
OL,10,Fby Ousmane Dembele's second-half
OL,11,Fpenalty.
OL,13,FArsenal defender Gabriel Magalhaes
OL,14,Ffired the last of his team's penalties
OL,15,Fover the bar, while Eberechi Eze also
OL,16,Fmissed his shot, handing PSG a 4-3
OL,17,Fshootout victory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
