OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780251070
OL,3,CArsenal miss out on Champions League
OL,4,Ctitle as PSG win on penalties
OL,6,FPSG landed the first psychological
OL,7,Fblow of the penalty shoot-out when
OL,8,Fthey won the coin toss with the shoot-
OL,9,Fout taking place in front of their
OL,10,Fsupporters at the Puskas Arena in
OL,11,FBudapest.
OL,13,FEze dragged his spot-kick wide before
OL,14,FDavid Raya provided Arsenal with a
OL,15,Flifeline when he saved from Nuno
OL,16,FMendes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
