OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780251070
OL,3,CArsenal miss out on Champions League
OL,4,Ctitle as PSG win on penalties
OL,6,FWith the shoot-out in the balance at 3-
OL,7,F3, Lucas Beraldo sent Raya the wrong
OL,8,Fway before Gabriel blazed over and
OL,9,FArsenal's dreams of following up their
OL,10,FPremier League title with a first
OL,11,FChampions League triumph came to a
OL,12,Fcrushing end.
OL,14,FWhile Arsenal fans will have hoped to
OL,15,Fcelebrate two historic titles this
OL,16,Fweekend, the Gunners will still take
OL,17,Fpart in an open-top bus parade
OL,18,Ftomorrow to celebrate the club's
OL,19,FPremier League title.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
