PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780251070
OL,3,CArsenal miss out on Champions League
OL,4,Ctitle as PSG win on penalties
OL,6,FThe parade, which is set to begin at
OL,7,F2pm at the Emirates Stadium in
OL,8,FHolloway and will follow a circular
OL,9,Froute through Islington.
OL,11,FIt has been estimated that as many as
OL,12,F500,000 people could be in attendance,
OL,13,Fwith the Metropolitan Police revealing
OL,14,Fon Friday that it is preparing for one
OL,15,Fof its largest policing operations of
OL,16,Fthe year.
OL,18,FSpeaking ahead of Saturday's showdown
OL,19,Fwith PSG, Arsenal forward Bukayo Saka
OL,20,Fsaid: "Personally I know exactly what
OL,21,Fit means to the fans.
OL,26,@|D@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
