FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780251070
OL,3,CArsenal miss out on Champions League
OL,4,Ctitle as PSG win on penalties
OL,6,F"It's been a long journey with some
OL,7,Fdisappointments along the way, but
OL,8,Fit's been worth it with the feeling to
OL,9,Fwin that Premier League.
OL,11,F"It felt like this last week it all
OL,12,Fbecame a reality. We could see how
OL,13,Fmuch it meant to the supporters. And
OL,14,Fthe parade is going to be the first
OL,15,Ftime we see a proper gathering of all
OL,16,Fthe Arsenal fans and we're very
OL,17,Fexcited.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
