OL,3,CArsenal miss out on Champions League
OL,4,Ctitle as PSG win on penalties
OL,6,F"But at the same time we're trying to
OL,7,Fstay focused on this game because
OL,8,Fwe're so excited, and so motivated to
OL,9,Fdo something special and make the
OL,10,Fparade even more crazy. This game is
OL,11,Four focus but after that we're going
OL,12,Fto enjoy it, too."
